only_totals: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT m.placa) FROM veiculo m WHERE m.codveiculo = (SELECT codveiculo FROM veiculo WHERE placa = m.placa ORDER BY COALESCE(dataatual, datainclusao) DESC LIMIT 1 );
initial_sync: SELECT veic.codveiculo, coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao) AS dataatual, veic.liberado,veic.placa,veic.bloqueadoadm from veiculo veic WHERE veic.codveiculo = (select veic2.codveiculo from veiculo veic2 where veic.placa = veic2.placa order by coalesce(veic2.dataatual, veic2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) ORDER BY coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao), codveiculo;
daily_sync: SELECT coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao) AS dataatual, veic.placa, veic.liberado, veic.bloqueadoadm, veic.obsbloq, mb.descricao AS MotivoBloqueio FROM veiculo veic LEFT OUTER JOIN motivobloqueio mb ON (veic.codmotivobloqueio = mb.codmotivobloqueio) WHERE coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao) >= '[$]' ORDER BY coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao) ASC;
working_table: SELECT veic.codveiculo, coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao) AS dataatual,veic.liberado,veic.placa,veic.bloqueadoadm from veiculo veic WHERE veic.codveiculo = (select veic2.codveiculo from veiculo veic2 where veic.placa = veic2.placa order by coalesce(veic2.dataatual, veic2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) ORDER BY coalesce(veic.dataatual, veic.datainclusao) DESC LIMIT 1;
total_by_date: SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT m.placa) FROM veiculo m WHERE  coalesce(m.dataatual, m.datainclusao) >= '[$]';
total_by_status_0: select 'QTDveiculos' as Tipo, 0 as Status,(SELECT count(veic.codveiculo)  FROM veiculo veic WHERE veic.codveiculo = (select veic2.codveiculo from veiculo veic2 where veic.placa = veic2.placa order by coalesce(veic2.dataatual, veic2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) AND veic.liberado = 'S' ) as QTD,current_date  as Data;
total_by_status_1: select  'QTDveiculos' as Tipo, 1 as Status, (SELECT count(veic.codveiculo) FROM veiculo veic  WHERE veic.codveiculo = (select veic2.codveiculo from veiculo veic2 where veic.placa = veic2.placa  order by coalesce(veic2.dataatual, veic2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 )  AND veic.liberado = 'N' AND ( veic.bloqueadoadm <> 'S' or veic.bloqueadoadm isnull) ) as QTD, current_date  as Data;
total_by_status_2: select  'QTDveiculos' as Tipo, 2 as Status, (SELECT count(veic.codveiculo) FROM veiculo veic  WHERE veic.codveiculo = (select veic2.codveiculo from veiculo veic2 where veic.placa = veic2.placa  order by coalesce(veic2.dataatual, veic2.datainclusao) desc limit 1 ) AND veic.liberado = 'N' AND  veic.bloqueadoadm = 'S') as QTD, current_date  as data;
